Package: mobspain
Title: Spanish Mobility Data Analysis Toolkit
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Prince", "Oppong Boakye", email = "prynx44@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Prince Oppong Boakye [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Prince Oppong Boakye <prynx44@gmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for analyzing Spanish mobility patterns using 
    MITMA (Ministry of Transport, Mobility and Urban Agenda) data. Provides 40+ 
    functions for data retrieval, advanced analytics, validation, and visualization. 
    Features include enhanced data access with intelligent caching, comprehensive 
    time series analysis with seasonal decomposition, advanced geospatial analysis 
    with hotspot detection, interactive dashboard creation, containment analysis, 
    anomaly detection, distance-decay modeling, machine learning integration, 
    and comprehensive data validation. Built on spanishoddata with performance 
    optimizations, intelligent fallback mechanisms, and production-ready tools.
